            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">If Auto-compute is off, this deduction can be entered manually per pay period.</p>

            <div class="mt-3">
                <label class="mb-1.5 block text-xs font-semibold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Scope Tags (comma separated)</label>
                <input type="text" id="deductionRuleScopeTags" placeholder="e.g. Head Office, Agency Staff" class="block w-full rounded-lg border-0 py-2.5 px-3 text-sm text-gray-900 ring-1 ring-inset ring-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-emerald-500 focus:outline-none dark:bg-gray-900 dark:text-white dark:ring-gray-600" />
